Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[奈莉奈 后篇]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀 你刚才都到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在枫在陪着她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看她的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆她... 情况有那么糟糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就像我告诉禀的那样...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以感受得到的 莉姆的情况很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的这份不安一定是她为莉姆...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是瞒不住奈莉奈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以 太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有这个方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.03,0:03:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我也有在寻找其他的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解奈莉奈的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有忘记莉可莉斯的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事要向禀保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能答应我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 又跑回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经知道了吧 普莉姆拉是人工生命体的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也知道不回魔界根本束手无策了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 禀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劝莉姆回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然劝了 但是她不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去莉姆会...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道 但是她不愿意又不能强行...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 禀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把莉姆送回魔界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再次失去重要的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从爸爸那里听说要救莉姆 必须要将她所有的感情重置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀大人好不容易才找回了莉姆的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸告诫我说不要告诉禀大人你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我无法隐瞒这么重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去见莉姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 莉姆她现在正因为生病...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 也知道得病的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及只有一个方法可以治好她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我才想陪在她的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只要再持续治疗一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许就会好转的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 还是再观察一段时间比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是等待什么都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己不行动的话 是无法保护所珍重的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 希望你们理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君...这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 希娅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去见莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...已经...不想再失去重要的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小禀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌不是我自己的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的我 根本无法唱出能打动人心的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:06:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌和这歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是属于我所珍重的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍重的人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个我 莉可莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知作为实验体的自己的境遇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却从未失去笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莉奈你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能快点好起来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照爸爸的说法 因为我的魔力太强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以身体很容易变差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 我来让奈莉奈精神起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说关于我的研究顺利的话 什么病都可以治好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以奈莉奈一定也会精神起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:08:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我来唱支歌给奈莉奈打气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说实验是非常痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是莉可莉斯却从没提起过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个坚强的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是个温柔的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到后来实验越来越频繁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉斯也就长住在研究所里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和莉姆似乎也是在那时候相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉和莉可莉斯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对莉姆而言 莉可莉斯就像是亲姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 普莉姆拉也有那样的亲人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那个叫莉可莉斯的女孩现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不在这个世上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉斯将自己的生命献给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治愈魔法也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 实在是束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用我的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我剩下的生命力移植给她 一定可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 莉可莉斯是奈莉奈大人的克隆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果将她的生命力返还给奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这样的话你会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样能救自己珍爱的人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀大人夸奖我唱的好的那首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在魔界被称为天使的声音的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是属于莉可莉斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 所以你刚才才会...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不光夺走了她的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还夺走了她所珍重的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不止这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连她更为珍重的东西也...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我再也不想失去所珍重的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令莉可莉斯丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:11:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在又让可以说是她的妹妹的莉姆遭遇不测的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 禀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想救莉姆 但是为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是无法坦率同意禀大人所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀大人听了我的话后 也开始迷茫起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 此时推了禀大人一把的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时雨学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说『如果真当莉姆是家人的话 就该去』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我没能说出口的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是禀大人下了前往魔界的决断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再次请求你 能让我见普莉姆拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不拿出勇气的话 一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去见莉姆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 普莉姆拉在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:12:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 小禀 我并不是想给你们留下这种回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要活着 只要活着的话就还能见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回我们的家 回你的家去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是禀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希娅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了吗 普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错是我 是禀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.54,0:14:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 如果现在普莉姆拉离开溶液的话她的生命就...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧 普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在控制自己的魔力...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 禀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉斯...姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后能见你一面 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 禀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.41,0:15:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里想着哪一颗是莉可莉斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉斯姐姐的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次我也没能好好道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没能道别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明被救了这么多次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我却什么都没为那孩子做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的 莉可莉斯姐姐一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小子 你这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样拍我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 看起来精神多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然还不是最佳状态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一周就可以上学了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有试过用治愈魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用做到那种地步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡一会就会好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上这么说 不快点恢复的话我很困扰的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么小禀你会困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问为什么...这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 有事想瞒着姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 该怎么说 没有亚沙学姐在身边的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 我是小禀你的靠山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是这样吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个这么逊的弟弟真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我很逊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙学姐 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去给你倒水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果觉得难受的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:18:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 都是因为小禀说了奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像笑得太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时雨学姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很喜欢禀大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀大人 你还记得这个公园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 和奈莉奈事隔八年的重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是我与禀大人第一次相遇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 八年前相遇时也是在...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一次是我第一次来人界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个公园里第一次遇见了您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:19:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八年前 见到禀大人的并不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后啊 那孩子叫禀 好温柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来奈莉奈的名字里也有这个音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 以后我就叫奈莉奈你琳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳？ 我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就算见不到面也不会寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去见他就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啦不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果有朝一日琳去人界的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要去见见他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替我去 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为了实现莉可莉丝的愿望而到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却...但却...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:20:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明想要彻底装成莉可莉斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在魔界研究所里...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 禀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才明白到莉可莉丝的愿望终于实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉丝一直想说那一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而剩下的就是我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉可莉斯走了 但我还是喜欢禀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份思念是只属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始的与禀大人的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是只属于奈莉奈的 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能更喜欢禀大人一些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.59,0:20:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不用回答
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能禀大人心里也有其他的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有这种女孩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是和我一样还没看清自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是才刚开始而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.46,0:21:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然喜欢禀大人的心意不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了让这分仰慕之情更加地深厚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还需要一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到这份感情不会输给任何人为止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 如果有一天我也能唱自己的歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您愿意听听吗 属于我的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一定要听
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这就作为到那时为止的约定

